g":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搞錯<br />\n有乜理由告唔入<br />\n<br />\n乜野叫有酒意無醉意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你又一個無中間<br />\n<br />\n飲酒就係得醉同清醒<br />\n<br />\n中間無慢慢變醉既過程既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係飲一杯就無啦啦訓低無知覺斷片架喇<br />\n<br />\n係咪咁樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少少醉wingwing 地同醉酒斷片你識唔識分</blockquote><br />\n咁你句有酒意無醉意質疑梗d咩野？？？？？？？？？"},{"pid":"52c7172a1d97d745806b8c3964d45f2ef510fe58","tid":372533,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"thank you sir唔該同學"},{"pid":"b35ff07afe25334ecd217f853fa0eaad72e84861","tid":372533,"uid":113429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:00:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b0ab183e66634212ba1372a3b326610b0c9b9b3","tid":372533,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:00:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f12c6c48321fde3d38b05b094aef9c95645c287e","tid":372533,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2ae8f4c3ac3050c484a252b349ad9a82f1d083a","tid":372533,"uid":122331,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搞錯<br />\n有乜理由告唔入<br />\n<br />\n乜野叫有酒意無醉意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條肥婆都搏俾人屌<br />\n既然係想俾人屌 而有人屌撚咗佢+<span style=\"color: red;\">屌嗰時條女又唔主動走</span><br />\n咁咪唔算強姦囉<br />\n<br />\n最多告得入個男護士獸交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你俾人強姦係咪會掙扎係咪會大叫係咪會走呀<br />\n而家你又要係大殺傷力肥婆 男護士又無綁住你<br />\n咪話隻抽 做少少掙扎都有得驗傷啦<br />\n<br />\n咪話樓主都講咗律師證明到肥婆無意願走<br />\n連肥婆都無提過佢曾經有一刻想走</blockquote><br />\n飲醉咗又點樣掙扎點樣大叫點樣走呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以你又assume咗個肥婆俾人強姦在先囉<br />\n<br />\n你又證明唔到佢被逼性交 佢無表示唔舒服 無走<br />\n辯方又證明到佢係想做愛<br />\n<br />\n無論係咪飲醉酒<br />\n你醉之前點都有意識掛？你真係飲一啖醉咗就話啫<br />\n同你飲酒條友你又無reject又無想走<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做你點挫得入強姦呀？"},{"pid":"637e4a2f2971fdf06844dc4e831d0cd9304d86ee","tid":372533,"uid":113429,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e149fca9aa8a1e5df0b29b03786811fe7dc5895b","tid":372533,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"八達通不設退款"},{"pid":"d29c910c68acdff49c8bc7408ba508d3053da7c6","tid":372533,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd286ed21626b06b3cc644e03072cf9206a32c25","tid":372533,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27ba97e9513c4b760cfbc32750360b9a4c3dd9e6","tid":372533,"uid":113429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08a51f79dbcc02a7758ba0d1a5e6a456b06fb39a","tid":372533,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"145磅，義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71cb555db7b2b4887c3a11bf50827842c34426f","tid":372533,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:05: